Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被“天壤的劫火”吞噬的话 就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 Hekate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼头…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的容器包容下了我的完全存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在契约之时已经感觉到了那种巨大…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 以后就什么时候都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别犯傻 赌命的行为是想做几次就做几次的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明把眼神移开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 夏娜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧露菲露米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狗屎运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微离开一下就发生了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 再稍微观察一下情势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救我啊 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 大姐头暂时留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知到底是福是祸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 诚实一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.07,0:23:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜 今天准备了晚饭 要来吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二学期我可能会加入竞争哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 池
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始 第二回合Start
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 把悠二带回来的时候明明还哭着谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说那是第一回合 我们彼此加油吧 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.31,0:24:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会输的 不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从今往后 也将一如既往地继续走下去
